      <item>
          <title>Elphie pulling Santa&#x27;s sleigh!</title>
          <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
          <author>Unknown</author>
          <link>https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2023/</link>
          <guid>https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2023/</guid>
          <description xml:base="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2023/">&lt;p&gt;This year I went for a bit of a different style. As I&#x27;ve been working on my black and white art for &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;projects&#x2F;quest&quot;&gt;my board games&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; I figured I&#x27;d get some practice in. This concept for this card came one evening and I managed to get the drawing done in a couple of hours. We had the cards printed on decent quality recycled card and they looked really good however I totally forgot to take a photo of the finished card! 🤦‍♂️ If I come across one in the future I&#x27;ll try to remember to snap it and update this post! 😅&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Front&quot; title=&quot;Front&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;front.4dad03112635ba75.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;front.7e8c286d18b3f524.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;front.4dad03112635ba75.webp 1024w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;front.93be2a6948270a2c.webp 2048w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Once again Neil came up with a great poem for the inside! 🎄&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Inside&quot; title=&quot;Inside&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inside.de855223c4eb3ed8.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inside.39d581a79e9f3872.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inside.de855223c4eb3ed8.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This year we&#x27;re supporting: &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.redcross.org.uk&#x2F;&quot;&gt;The British Red Cross&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. I reused a little &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;inktober-beast&#x2F;&quot;&gt;sketch of us&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; at Filey Bay from this years &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;series&#x2F;inktober-2023&quot;&gt;Inktober&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Back&quot; title=&quot;Back&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;back.b0170305da0d7ae5.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;back.b1ed9c439f60ee11.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;back.b0170305da0d7ae5.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

</description>
